     9→/**
    10→ * Plugin Name: AdminPulse
    11→ * Description: A glanceable dashboard widget showing your WordPress site health status
    12→ * Version: 1.0.0
    13→ * Requires at least: 6.2
    14→ * Requires PHP: 8.0
